<div class="com-share" data-id="20352" data-title="《盖楼遇到了不规则场地？那就把大楼“折”起来吧》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/20352/medium/20352.jpg?1452079886" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/20352.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
